legs.start_address: Hocaömer, Atatürk Cd. No:21, 02100 Adıyaman Merkez/Adıyaman, Turkey

steps.html_instructions:
Make a U-turn at Atatürk Cd.
Continue to follow D360

Turn right onto Atatürk Blv./D850
Continue to follow D850
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Termik Cd.

Slight right onto Kayseri Kahramanmaraş Yolu/D815
Continue to follow D815

Turn left onto Kayseri Malatya Yolu/D300
Continue to follow D300
Keep left at the fork and merge onto D260/D300

Keep right at the fork and merge onto Kayseri Kırşehir Yolu/D260
Continue to follow D260
Take the ramp to Kırıkkale Kırşehir Yolu/D765

Slight right onto Kırıkkale Çankırı Yolu/D765
Continue to follow D765

Slight right onto Ankara Çankırı Yolu/D765
Continue to follow D765
Turn left to stay on Maruf Köyü Yolu
